### Playback History API テスト

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
@episodeId = YOUR_EPISODE_ID_HERE

### 再生履歴一覧を取得
GET {{baseUrl}}/me/playback-history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 再生履歴一覧を取得（完了済みのみ）
GET {{baseUrl}}/me/playback-history?completed=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 再生履歴一覧を取得（未完了のみ）
GET {{baseUrl}}/me/playback-history?completed=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 再生履歴一覧を取得（ページネーション）
GET {{baseUrl}}/me/playback-history?limit=10&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 再生履歴を更新（再生位置のみ）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/episodes/{{episodeId}}/playback
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "progressMs": 60000
}

### 再生履歴を更新（完了）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/episodes/{{episodeId}}/playback
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "progressMs": 180000,
  "completed": true
}

### 再生履歴を削除
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/episodes/{{episodeId}}/playback
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
